title: Beyond The Valley Of The Dolls (1970)
description: A hip and happenin&#039; all girl rock group head to LA to claim lead-singer Kelly&#039;s inheritance and make it (and make it) in LA. They immediately fall under the spell of rock&#039;n&#039;roll Svengali, the &#039;Teen Tycoon&#039; of rock Ronnie &#039;Z-Man&#039; Barzell, and other rapacious Hollywood party types as lustful porno actress Ashley St Ives, ravenous lesbian Roxanne and shady lawyer Porter Hall. Soon the girls fall into a morass of drugs and deceit as their recording success soars. It takes several tragedies to make them stop and think... but is it too late?
